WEBVTT

00:01.757 --> 00:04.859
I am ice.

00:05.859 --> 00:07.773
I move slowly.

00:08.958 --> 00:11.209
I keep the world cool.

00:13.114 --> 00:15.555
Well, I used to.

00:16.861 --> 00:19.383
But humans keep warming this planet.

00:21.183 --> 00:22.520
I try to warn you.

00:23.683 --> 00:27.334
I send pieces of me thundering into the ocean.

00:28.257 --> 00:30.085
You do nothing.

00:32.789 --> 00:34.725
I raise sea levels.

00:36.681 --> 00:38.649
You do nothing.

00:41.283 --> 00:43.863
It has taken you decades to notice.

00:45.309 --> 00:49.171
Perhaps I'm not so slow after all.

